trans-unit.source: Represents a find request sent by a client.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en Finn forespørselen som ble sendt av en klient.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext"></xref> class using the specified <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindCriteria"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext"> </xref> klasse parametersettet med de angitte <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindCriteria"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Enables the discovery service to send results back to the client as they are received.
trans-unit.target: Aktiverer søketjeneste å sende resultatene tilbake til klienten som de mottas.

trans-unit.source: The endpoint discovery metadata to send back to the client.
trans-unit.target: Discovery-metadata for endepunktet til å sende tilbake til klienten.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindCriteria"></xref> associated with the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext"></xref> sent by the client.
trans-unit.target: Henter den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindCriteria"> </xref> knyttet til den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext"> </xref> sendt av klienten.

trans-unit.source: The find criteria sent by the client.
trans-unit.target: Finn vilkårene som er sendt av klienten.

trans-unit.source: Called after the user adds an endpoint to the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext"></xref> by calling <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext.AddMatchingEndpoint*>.
trans-unit.target: Kalles etter at brukeren legger til et endepunkt som den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext"> </xref> ved å kalle <xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext.AddMatchingEndpoint*>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Discovery.FindRequestContext.AddMatchingEndpoint*>

trans-unit.source: The endpoint discovery metadata to send back to the client.
trans-unit.target: Discovery-metadata for endepunktet til å sende tilbake til klienten.
